done

void done()
Called when WPS is ready for further requests. No WPS methods may called until after this method returns, once a WPS method which uses a callback has been called. In other words, only one WPS operation may be active at any time.

handleError

WPSContinuation handleError(WPSReturnCode error)
Called when WPS encounters an error.

Parameters:
error -
Returns:
WPS_CONTINUE to retry, or WPS_STOP. Note WPS may choose not to retry even if WPS_CONTINUE is returned.
